      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>LYF 香瓜子葵花子春节促销</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n        color: #8B0000;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    header, main, footer {\n        width: 100%;\n    }\n    .container {\n        max-width: 800px;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        padding: 1rem;\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n    }\n    section, nav, aside, div {\n        margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        padding: 1rem;\n        background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n    }\n    h1, h2, h3 {\n        margin-top: 0;\n        color: #D32F2F;\n    }\n    p {\n        margin: 0.5rem 0;\n    }\n    ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        padding: 0;\n        margin: 0;\n    }\n    ul li {\n        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        padding-left: 1rem;\n        position: relative;\n    }\n    ul li::before {\n        content: \"•\";\n        color: #FBC02D;\n        position: absolute;\n        left: 0;\n    }\n    .price-box {\n        background-color: #FBC02D;\n        color: #8B0000;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .promotion-tags {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 0.5rem;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n    }\n    .promotion-tags span {\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        font-size: 0.9rem;\n    }\n    .buy-channel label {\n        display: block;\n        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n    }\n    .buy-channel input {\n        width: 100%;\n        padding: 0.5rem;\n        margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        border: 1px solid #ccc;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n    }\n    .buy-channel button {\n        padding: 0.7rem 1rem;\n        margin-right: 0.5rem;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n    .btn-cart {\n        background-color: #FBC02D;\n        color: #8B0000;\n    }\n    .btn-buy {\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n    }\n    .cart-panel {\n        background-color: #F4F4F5;\n    }\n    .cart-panel button {\n        background-color: #D32F2F;\n        color: #FFFFFF;\n        padding: 0.7rem;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    nav ul li {\n        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n    }\n    nav ul li a {\n        text-decoration: none;\n        color: #8B0000;\n        padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;\n        display: inline-block;\n    }\n    .coupon-box button {\n        background-color: #FBC02D;\n        color: #8B0000;\n        padding: 0.7rem 1rem;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 600px) {\n        .buy-channel button {\n            width: 100%;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n        }\n        .promotion-tags {\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<main class=\"container\">\n    <section id=\"hero\" class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>春节佳礼 · LYF 香瓜子葵花子</h1>\n        <p>欢享团聚时刻，点击查看更多美味详情</p>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"product-spec\" class=\"product-spec\">\n        <h2>产品规格</h2>\n        <p>500g*2袋，原味/五香可选，产地内蒙古，保质期12个月</p>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"selling-points\" class=\"selling-points\">\n        <h2>核心卖点</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>精选优质原料</li>\n            <li>新鲜烘焙工艺</li>\n            <li>独立小包装设计</li>\n        </ul>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"price-box\" class=\"price-box\">\n        <h2>限时优惠价 ¥29.9</h2>\n        <p>原价 ¥39.9，立省 ¥10</p>\n    </section>\n    <div id=\"promotion-tags\" class=\"promotion-tags\">\n        <span>限时促销</span>\n        <span>热销商品</span>\n        <span>库存紧张</span>\n    </div>\n    <section id=\"countdown-timer\" class=\"countdown-timer\">\n        <h3>优惠倒计时</h3>\n        <p>剩余 02:15:45</p>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"buy-channel\" class=\"buy-channel\">\n        <label for=\"quantity\">选择购买数量</label>\n        <input type=\"number\" id=\"quantity\" name=\"quantity\" min=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <button class=\"btn-cart\">加入购物车</button>\n        <button class=\"btn-buy\">立即购买</button>\n    </section>\n    <aside id=\"cart-panel\" class=\"cart-panel\">\n        <h2>购物车</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li>LYF 香瓜子葵花子 × 2</li>\n        </ul>\n        <button>去结算</button>\n    </aside>\n    <nav id=\"category-nav\" class=\"category-nav\">\n        <h2>春节零食分类</h2>\n        <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">瓜子</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">坚果</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">糖果</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"#\">糕点</a></li>\n        </ul>\n    </nav>\n    <section id=\"coupon-box\" class=\"coupon-box\">\n        <h2>领取优惠券</h2>\n        <button>立即领取</button>\n    </section>\n</main>\n</body>\n</html>"
    }
